Manga
A manga adaptation, illustrated by Bunko Matsuura, was serialized on Ichijinsha's Zero-Sum Online website from March 19, 2020, to March 18, 2022. As of January 2022, the series' individual chapters have been collected into three  volumes. In October 2022, it was announced that the manga adaptation had been cancelled due to the poor health of the artist. A new manga adaptation, illustrated by Akiko Kawano, began serialization in Ichijinsha's Monthly Comic Zero Sum magazine on June 28, 2023.
Seven Seas Entertainment is also publishing the manga adaptation in English.
